node.text:
Blue Steel. Little League dad. High school graduate.
On the five-year anniversary of being selected by the Ducks, @maxjones98 pokes fun at himself in the various Draft portraits he took that day in 2016. #FlyTogether

Unforgettable memories made right here at @hondacenter.

Big 🧡 to @honda.  #FlyTogether

node.text: Welcome to #NHLDraft week! Our last few have been 💪. We are one of two NHL teams (NYR) to have each of their top selections in both 2019 (Zegras) and 2020 (Drysdale) play in the NHL. Drysdale was the only defensemen selected in 2020 to play in the NHL in 2020-21. #FlyTogether #DucksDraft presented by @honda.
